cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.RO 

The paper proposes a method for improving pedestrian detection using deep convolutional neural networks, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of gated feature extraction also involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. Additionally, the paper involves experimentation and evaluation of the proposed method, which could fall under robotics (cs.RO) and neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories.
